{
  "stem": "3653.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was still-- the war was still not finished because the war was finished in '45, but this was before.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the Russians was there, and they check everybody with a passport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't have any passport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I told them I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said in Russian, Jew, no Jew, you have to have a passport.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they took me to the office with the Russian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I told them, I told the officer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Let's take a look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm from here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was hidden here until-- and I don't have any document.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he wants me to go with me and to show where was it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And already he talks to me in Russian, and the people, the Polish people around me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told them in Russian, you see the people here?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would know I'm there, I wouldn't be alive today.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I can't go with you, because later they'll killed the Polish people hiding me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He gave me a cigarette.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave me food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just tell my name, and they wouldn't bother anybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went there to Lublin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Came to Lublin, was already a lot of Jewish people there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was already a committee, a Jewish committee, from the Joint and the HIAS there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the two guys with me, they went in the police, the Polish police.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I didn't want to go to Polish police.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'd like to do something-- business, you know, to make a living.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What I needed Polish police there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I start little by little, little by little there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure, because when I saw the Russian people who came in the village when I was hidden there.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
